* Dinobot snarled as he heard Tavatron's faint words, how could she be so 
laied back about this? The enemy was coming, or so it felt.
He looked at her then back at the doors, perhaps she was right, perhaps it 
would be wise to just let Liono call them when the battle struck.
Dinobot growled as he looked Tavatron and made eye contact, he looked away, 
he didn't mean to do that.
He sighed and ran his hand over the door's smooth surface one last time, 
there would come a time when he was called to battle this day. But not now.
Dinobot snarled...*

" Where were you leading me?"
